snippet.title: TV MADness | MAD Parody Video List | Cartoon Network
snippet.description: They say imitation is the sincerest form of flattery. If that's true, then MAD must love TV, because they've mashed up, spoofed and skewered every show worth watching. Let the MADness begin!

snippet.title: Bowled Over
snippet.description: Cannonbolt barrels into Princess Attea and the bounty hunters. Watch more Ben 10 Omniverse on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Grim and Dracula Golfing
snippet.description: Grim faces off against Dracula in miniature golf. Watch more of The Grim Adventures of Billy & Mandy on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Heavy Handed
snippet.description: Gravattack uses his gravity powers to lock down the enemy. Watch more Ben 10 Omniverse on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: School Play
snippet.description: Eric finds out the school play is more dangerous than he bargained for. Watch more Sidekick on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Animal Ghosts
snippet.description: Mordecai, Rigby and Benson must work together to survive a series of Animal Ghost attacks! Watch more Regular Show on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: ApeTrully Rescue
snippet.description: When ApeTrully is trapped inside a giant skeleton, Lin Chung must find a way to rescue him. Watch more Hero 108 on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Attack on Eagle Spire
snippet.description: The Crocodiles hire the Ravens to trick the Wolves into attacking the Eagle Spires. But it is all part of an elaborate plot to harm both the Lions, Eagles and Wolves. Laval and Eris must act quickly to save the day.

snippet.title: Bad Memories
snippet.description: After Johnny loses his memory, Susan and Dukey must track him down. Watch more Johnny Test on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Balancing Act
snippet.description: The Wolves are still stealing CHI and everyone else has very little. When a load of CHI falls into the Gorge of Eternal Depth, Laval, Eris and Gorzan must try to retrieve it. But the Wolves are more powerful than ever.
